{
  "texts": [
    "(1) While getting your driver's license in the US, you are asked to register as a voter.",
    "Your basic demographic information, including date of birth, gender, ethnicity, residency, as well as your party of affiliation are recorded and stored in a public database.",
    "Back home that day, you purchase Atlas Shrugged by Ayn Rand; your purchase is stored on the Amazon database together with your purchase history and your personal data.",
    "A data aggregator purchases the data from Amazon and gains access to the public database, merging the two datasets and generating an augmented VR file.",
    "A political campaign acquires the augmented VR file and generates predictions about your voting behaviour based on your purchasing behavior and other personal information."
  ]
}